ordie-greep-among-line-up-additions-as-day-splits-revealed-3831133">第二波的阵容</a>，并透露了<a class="editor-rtfLink" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Nine-Inch-Nails" target="_blank" rel="noopener">九英寸的指甲</a>， <a class="editor-rtfLink" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Geordie-Greep" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Geordie Greep</a> ，坏神经，ChloéCaillet和Kingfishr将表演。</p><p> <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fmad-cool-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F2254495" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处的门票</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mad-cool-2025-nine-inch-nails-and-geordie-greep-among-line-up-additions-as-day-splits-revealed-3831133">在这里找到一天的分裂</a>。</p><p>除了宣布与早午餐Electronik的合作伙伴关系外，还分享了Vibra Mahou赢得2025年Mad Cool Talent的艺术家。该计划有助于为新兴人才提供支持和平台，并为他们提供了在音乐节上表演的机会。 2025年透露了六名获奖者：Ashleys，Jøl，Blanche小姐，Lavin，RodrigoRamírez和Will Kolak。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a>的2024年Mad Cool Saw表演，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">带给我地平线</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">粉碎的南瓜</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">垃圾</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janelle-monae">JanelleMonáe</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nothing-but-thieves">除了小偷</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-odell">汤姆·奥德尔</a>等。在此处查看<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/mad-cool-festival-2024-day-one-photos-dua-lipa-janelle-monae-smashing-pumpkins-3773899">活动综述</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brunch-electronik-announce-full-line-up-for-mad-cool-2025-3852071">早午餐Electronik宣布Mad Cool 2025的完整阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
